title: North Macedonia Natural Gas Imports From Russia
description: Natural Gas Imports from Russia in Macedonia increased to 882 Terajoule in August from 484 Terajoule in July of 2022. Natural Gas Imports from Russia in Macedonia averaged 780.36 Terajoule from 2013 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 2049 Terajoule in January of 2017 and a record low of 69 Terajoule in August of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for Macedonia Natural Gas Imports From Russia.
author: EUROSTAT
